- A 60-year-old Saudi male, non-healthcare worker from Jazan (Jizan) [Jīzan region] with a history of pre-existing co-morbidities. [Reported as a newly confirmed case on 13 Oct 2017 at which time he was noted to be in stable condition. Classified as a primary case with a history of direct contact with camels in the 14 days preceding onset of illness. - Mod.MPP]

